{"id":13837,"date":"2022-09-29T10:02:15","date_gmt":"2022-09-29T03:02:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13837"},"modified":"2022-10-01T10:03:21","modified_gmt":"2022-10-01T03:03:21","slug":"nhung-loi-ich-khi-su-dung-xe-lai-dien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/nhung-loi-ich-khi-su-dung-xe-lai-dien\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00f4 t\u00f4 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe hybrid c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u0103ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m x\u0103ng, d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n mang t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00e1c cho ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu.<\/div>\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body\">\n<p><strong>Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i trong xe hybrid. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, SUV Honda CR-V Hybrid s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kho\u1ea3ng 120g\/km kh\u00ed CO2. Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hybrid cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u1edf ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n pin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i x\u1ebf quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>T\u0103ng ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/cr-v-hybrid-comfort-compare-3-8571.jpg\" data-desc=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n\" data-index=\"0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/cr-v-hybrid-comfort-compare-3-8571.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n \u1ea3nh 1\" data-image-id=\"3312882\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"900\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/cr-v-hybrid-comfort-compare-3-8571.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>D\u00f9 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng, xe hybrid v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n n\u1ea1p nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u. Tr\u00ean Honda CR-V hybrid, khi di chuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 40 d\u1eb7m\/gi\u1edd (64,3 km\/h), chi\u1ebfc xe ti\u00eau hao kho\u1ea3ng 4,43 l\/100km. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7y b\u00ecnh, n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i h\u01a1n 600 d\u1eb7m (965,6 km) v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cao h\u01a1n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Xe hybrid th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u1edfi c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tin c\u1eady nh\u01b0 Audi, BMW, Honda, Chevrolet. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cao h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, ch\u00fang c\u00f2n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4, gi\u00fap n\u00f3 gi\u1eef gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u nh\u1edd phanh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/regenerative-braking-5521.jpg\" data-desc=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n\" data-index=\"1\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/regenerative-braking-5521.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n \u1ea3nh 2\" data-image-id=\"3312883\" data-width=\"1440\" data-height=\"864\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/regenerative-braking-5521.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng phanh t\u00e1i sinh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn trong ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4. Ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u00f2ng xe thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 hybrid. B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n cho xe \u00f4 t\u00f4, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea1p phanh.<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe hybrid, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, Honda CR-V Hybrid c\u00f3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 EV Drive (ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n), Engine Drive (ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y) v\u00e0 Hybrid Drive (khai th\u00e1c s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai) \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Xe hybrid s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/benefits-of-a-hybrid-vehicle-that-go-beyond-fuel-efficiency-8754.jpg\" data-desc=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n\" data-index=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/benefits-of-a-hybrid-vehicle-that-go-beyond-fuel-efficiency-8754.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe lai \u0111i\u1ec7n \u1ea3nh 3\" data-image-id=\"3312881\" data-width=\"525\" data-height=\"390\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_15\/benefits-of-a-hybrid-vehicle-that-go-beyond-fuel-efficiency-8754.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>\u00d4 t\u00f4 lai \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n sang x\u0103ng v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n hay ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ee7 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 hybrid cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee9c pin c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n tr\u00ean xe. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, khi pin y\u1ebfu, hybrid s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng x\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi s\u1ea1c pin.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, xe hybrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u0103ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c l\u00e1i xe. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, xe hybrid ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Ch\u00fang mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00f4 t\u00f4 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe hybrid c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u0103ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m x\u0103ng, d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n mang t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00e1c cho ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu. Gi\u1ea3m [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13630,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13837"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13837"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13837\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13838,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13837\/revisions\/13838"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13630"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13837"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13837"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13837"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=13837"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}